You can't miss the gas stations on the route, because here you can change the car, even though in most cases the car that you just have is sufficient.
The cars are divided into three categories.
The sports cars are well suited for the urban areas, the strong American limousines for the straight highways and exotic super sports cars for the technical rides, for example on the Serpentines in the mountain range.
Hand in hand with the mode of the history of the game, the task mode (requirements) - that is the race in the individual localities you know from history.
